1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:32,069
=Episode 27=
(You are my god.)

3
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:36,240
(To die for you
would be my greatest honor.)

4
00:00:37,700 --> 00:00:38,780
Still fighting?

5
00:00:39,300 --> 00:00:40,980
You're the only one left!

6
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:42,259
Who says

7
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:44,180
he's the only one left?

8
00:00:55,260 --> 00:00:55,940
Immortal,

9
00:00:57,420 --> 00:00:58,140
Baobao's...

10
00:00:58,420 --> 00:00:59,780
Baobao told me everything.

11
00:01:01,060 --> 00:01:02,100
Protect her.

12
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,500
I'm going to save Xi.

13
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:11,339
Go, now!

14
00:01:11,340 --> 00:01:12,900
Don't let Ye Zhao ruin the ritual!

15
00:01:15,900 --> 00:01:17,740
Anyone who crosses this line

16
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:19,700
dies!

17
00:01:47,260 --> 00:01:48,660
Interesting.

18
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,380
So I can't control you after all.

19
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:55,580
Xi!

20
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:01,380
Zhao, I'm right here.

21
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:05,500
I've already taken over Xi's body.

22
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:07,380
In no time at all,

23
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:10,740
I'll devour her soul completely.

24
00:02:11,060 --> 00:02:14,140
After that, there will be
no Xi left in this world!

25
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:22,660
Honey, you're so heartless.

26
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:25,300
You attacked me the second you got here.

27
00:02:26,140 --> 00:02:27,500
If you don't have a body,

28
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:30,300
then go cultivate one yourself.

29
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:31,580
You get to live,

30
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:33,660
but someone else has to die?

31
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,580
How does that make any sense?

32
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:39,780
Little immortal,

33
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,580
what do you expect me to do?

34
00:02:43,460 --> 00:02:44,860
Be like you?

35
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:47,300
Care about all mankind?

36
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:50,060
Save the world from suffering?

37
00:02:52,540 --> 00:02:54,860
I'm a demon.

38
00:02:56,820 --> 00:03:01,140
I don't have your kind heart.

39
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,539
If I didn't spare the good ones,

40
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:06,140
if I killed every demon on sight,

41
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:10,020
would you even be here now?

42
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:13,260
Blame your soft heart.

43
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,420
Get him.

44
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:38,339
Today,

45
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:39,579
I'm going to make

46
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:41,340
the heavens obey my will!

47
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:43,700
Dream on!

48
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:10,060
Little immortal,

49
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:12,060
didn't you want to kill me?

50
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:15,780
Come on.

51
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:18,220
Stab right here.

52
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:19,380
Do it.

53
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:21,860
Go ahead.

54
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,220
Kill me.

55
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,620
You really did it?

56
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:36,540
Zhao,

57
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:37,980
that hurts.

58
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:42,100
Where'd all that brave talk go?

59
00:05:44,660 --> 00:05:48,259
♪For you,
I brushed the snow from your robes♪

60
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:51,179
♪I crossed mountains and seas
just to see you once♪

61
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:52,740
Mind your own business.

62
00:05:53,050 --> 00:06:00,490
♪I once fell asleep to the sound
of rain beneath the southern stars♪

63
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:01,740
Faster!

64
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:02,540
Chief Zhang!

65
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:04,979
Quick!

66
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:06,660
Drive Butcher Zhang away! Protect Xi!

67
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:08,219
Sorry for making everyone worry.

68
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,060
No,

69
00:06:09,780 --> 00:06:11,339
Xi, are you okay?

70
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:12,539
Are you hurt anywhere?

71
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,859
I just called everyone over to help.
Where's Butcher Zhang?

72
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:16,240
Just wait till I get my hands on him!

73
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,859
♪Travel a thousand miles to you♪

74
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:19,300
Xi...

75
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:22,239
♪You are a night of falling petals♪

76
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:26,439
♪Gone in a blink,
you fade to the horizon♪

77
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:31,539
♪Telling me not to long for you♪

78
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:32,860
Xi...

79
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:40,180
Die!

80
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:42,380
The full moon is here.

81
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:03,980
(Dexin Hall)
(Xi!)

82
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:14,980
You lost again.

83
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:18,420
Again! I wasn't using my left hand.
I'll switch to my right!

84
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:21,860
I'm not playing with you anymore.
You're terrible, and you cheat!

85
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:24,420
Mother!

86
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:26,060
Mother,

87
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:28,859
look at the great general.

88
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:30,180
He cheats at arm wrestling.

89
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,060
Your Highness, I wasn't cheating!

90
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:35,420
It's strategy.

91
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:37,100
Again!

92
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:39,180
Sure. Bring it on!

93
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:43,980
- I'm done!
- Stop!

94
00:07:45,660 --> 00:07:46,380
Baobao!

95
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:48,500
Xi!

96
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:51,180
Zhao!

97
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:55,740
Come here.

98
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:00,220
Come. Sit.

99
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:08,230
I wish it could always stay like this.

100
00:08:11,740 --> 00:08:13,220
Now that the demon root is gone,

101
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,620
the Verdant Decay disease is gone too.

102
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:18,180
The flower slaves are human again.

103
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:20,300
Heaven itself

104
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:25,180
has allowed us to love each other.

105
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:27,740
Xi!

106
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,820
Wake up, Xi!

107
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,500
Little Immortal,

108
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:34,220
love is just a foolish illusion.

109
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:37,060
You're a god.

110
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:40,940
So why are you still bound
by worldly desires,

111
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:42,420
unable to escape?

112
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:46,060
You're pathetic!

113
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:53,820
Xi,

114
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:55,100
wake up!

115
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:58,620
Wake up, Xi!

116
00:08:58,980 --> 00:09:00,420
It's useless.

117
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:03,540
I've already sealed away her soul.

118
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:05,300
She can't hear you.

119
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:08,420
She's living her sweetest dream.

120
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:11,540
From now on, the world will be quiet.

121
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:14,500
Our family

122
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:18,540
can finally be together forever.

123
00:09:22,660 --> 00:09:24,660
This really has been a long story.

124
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:32,540
Xi,

125
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,860
wake up!

126
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,740
I know you're still in there!

127
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:37,780
Xi!

128
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:08,940
Xi.

129
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:12,540
Xi.

130
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:18,180
Xi.

131
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,180
Mother!

132
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:25,540
Your Highness!

133
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:27,940
Your Highness!

134
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:28,979
My lady!

135
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:29,859
Xi!

136
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:30,820
Your Highness!

137
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:37,960
♪It bids farewell to another blue sky♪

138
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:40,319
♪Gone in a blink,
you fade to the horizon♪

139
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,600
♪Telling me not to long for you♪

140
00:10:44,220 --> 00:10:45,540
Why am I here?

141
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:50,379
♪Counting every moment,
unwilling to pause♪

142
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:54,420
Stay away from those flower slaves!

143
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:58,940
That ritual can erase
the demon root for good.

144
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:01,420
If you have that flower slave refine me,

145
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:03,060
you'll die too!

146
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:04,820
(For my body, )

147
00:11:05,380 --> 00:11:07,340
(you really planned
all the way to this point.)

148
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:10,020
Hua Hui,

149
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:13,540
get the hell out!

150
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:31,260
It's useless.

151
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:33,660
You can't kill me.

152
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:36,340
The demon root will grow
another demon heart.

153
00:11:40,820 --> 00:11:41,940
Wait.

154
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:44,700
Hua Hui's demon root

155
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:47,820
was hidden inside the eyes of my soul.

156
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,820
No wonder

157
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:57,180
I can see the fate of people
who are about to die.

158
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:14,660
Hua Hui, you finally showed yourself!

159
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:23,060
You actually got

160
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:24,820
your demon root cut off by that cutie,

161
00:12:25,860 --> 00:12:27,540
and lost control of your body.

162
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:29,940
Little immortal,

163
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:32,140
don't celebrate too soon.

164
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:33,940
If I die,

165
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:36,180
Xi won't survive either!

166
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:43,660
The one you killed

167
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:45,460
was your lover

168
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:47,900
and your other self!

169
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:49,340
What are you talking about?

170
00:12:50,380 --> 00:12:54,180
We were always one!

171
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:58,540
(You and I were one to begin with.)

172
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,580
(We cultivated together in Baihua Hall
for a thousand years.,)

173
00:13:01,740 --> 00:13:03,859
(sustained by He Xi's flesh and blood)

174
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:05,540
(and gained consciousness,)

175
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:08,660
(ready to bloom and ascend.)

176
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:13,459
You little weed,

177
00:13:13,460 --> 00:13:14,499
Master said

178
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:17,260
you've been in this temple
nearly a thousand years.

179
00:13:17,620 --> 00:13:19,619
Plain dew isn't enough for you.

180
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:21,060
You insist on drinking my blood.

181
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:22,940
You're so picky.

182
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,139
Oh, you.

183
00:13:24,140 --> 00:13:25,580
When the Red Spider Lily

184
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:27,300
blooms, there are no leaves.

185
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:29,300
When the leaves grow,
there are no flowers.

186
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:33,300
Flower and leaf can never meet.

187
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:37,460
You're one fussy little plant.

188
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:40,460
If I bloom,

189
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:42,900
you'll die!

190
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:45,219
I gave up my body

191
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:46,660
to help you become a god.

192
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:48,540
And I

193
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:52,900
was left a demon heart without a body!

194
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:57,300
That still doesn't excuse
all the evil you've done!

195
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:17,420
Xi!

196
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:22,389
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

197
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:25,239
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

198
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,979
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

199
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,609
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

200
00:14:29,610 --> 00:14:35,210
(Perhaps, if I reincarnate,)

201
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:36,859
(I can rid myself of this demon heart.)

202
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:39,619
(I will definitely
come back to find you.)

203
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:42,469
(You must wait for me.)

204
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:45,069
♪If in a dream♪

205
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:49,859
♪I can hear your voice♪

206
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:51,619
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

207
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:54,270
♪Let it be us♪

208
00:14:54,490 --> 00:14:57,209
♪drawing endlessly close♪

209
00:14:57,210 --> 00:14:58,859
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

210
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:04,519
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

211
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:06,059
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

212
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:08,809
♪Not even in time♪

213
00:15:08,810 --> 00:15:11,779
♪to tell you how I feel♪

214
00:15:11,780 --> 00:15:14,329
♪If the rain won't stop♪

215
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:18,969
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

216
00:15:18,970 --> 00:15:21,579
♪Let love go on♪

217
00:15:21,580 --> 00:15:28,690
♪Until forever♪
